              Life Love Dance
            
              (Mixed Signals/Left Ear Records / Left Ear Records)
label: Mixed Signals/Left Ear Records / Left Ear Records
description:
What a find from Left Ear?! LITIA=LOE’s darker toned and sexy Chicago body music rides again on reissue of their sole, 1994 album - a massive RIYL Virgo, Jamie Principle, Chris & Cosey, Jamal Moss, Noleian Reusse, New Order, Electribe 101

Prised from obscurity by Naarm’s Left Ear Records, the sultry finesse of ‘Life Love Dance’ returns like a rare comet on 30 year orbit from its first sighting; a coveted 12” issued in 1994 as one of two releases on LITIA=LOE’s Chicago-based Façade... more
